OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fwill soon die out this evening leaving
OL,7,Fa dry and mostly clear night across
OL,8,Fthe region, with lighter winds than of
OL,9,Flate. However, some patchy cloud may
OL,10,Fdevelop towards the morning. A frost
OL,11,Fforming in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FEaster Monday will be dry and
OL,14,Fsettled with some sunshine, this
OL,15,Fturning a little hazy at times. There
OL,16,Fwill be a southerly breeze, but
OL,17,Ffeeling pleasant in the sun.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
