OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday and Wednesday look dry with
OL,7,Fsome very warm sunshine, though breezy
OL,8,Fat first. Rain arriving on Wednesday
OL,9,Fnight, clearing to colder weather on
OL,10,FThursday with sunshine and blustery
OL,11,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
